{"tid":2298080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地真光女書院辯論隊女導師確診涉跳舞群組　曾參與活動學生停課14日","createTime":"2020-11-23T20:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:22:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef35d04d44b38a790b176e61a03a2f5c861b65e5","tid":2298080,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T20:45:34.000Z","msg":"衞生署衞生防護中心今日（23日）公布新增73宗確診個案，63宗屬本地感染，跳舞群組確診者佔50人，其中一宗為真光中學課外活動女導師（第5,680宗），與她一起參與活動的學生要接受檢測和暫停上學。<br />\n<br />\n不過，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君在今日下午的疫情記者會上，回答說不肯定該名確診者於哪一間真光擔任導師。<br />\n<br />\n本港共有4間真光中學，據稱校方今日傍晚通知家長，該名確診女導師為油麻地真光女書院的中文辯論隊導師，該校並宣布今日起全校停課2日，曾出席相關活動的學生將停課14日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2810379/dicn20150901401_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2810379%2Fdicn20150901401_1024_1024.jpg&h=0c1adb2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c00cc4656af634f95991d573257310f94f975946","tid":2298080,"uid":171786,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T21:03:12.000Z","msg":"真係慘，全校都知佢叫鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2018987653a8ef02280257d3baa7a2266613c150","tid":2298080,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c00cc4656af634f95991d573257310f94f975946","tid":2298080,"uid":171786,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T21:03:12.000Z","msg":"真係慘，全校都知佢叫鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T21:11:59.000Z","msg":"女導師 &ne; 女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3df7816d34ad708998301491bc0eff6dcc8943","tid":2298080,"uid":44298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c00cc4656af634f95991d573257310f94f975946","tid":2298080,"uid":171786,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T21:03:12.000Z","msg":"真係慘，全校都知佢叫